To Deploy a Python Application on AWS Cloud we need to follow steps:

step1.) Create EC2 instance on AWS.
step2.) take access the EC2 instance by using your host machine.
	-for taking the acccess we need the security key.
	-we login in EC2 instanse with the help of SSH.

step3.) after getting the access of EC2 instance, pull the python code from git/local_system/etc.
step4.) now install python,pip,flask in your EC2 instance.
	- apt-get update
	- apt-get install python
	- apt install python3-pip
	- pip3 onstall flask

step5.) run our python Application.
	- python filename. (execute python code)
step6.) use your EC2 instance IP to view your python application on browser.
